I"‚V<h2 id="attributes">Attributes</h2>

<p>PlayerEx adds fully functional attributes to the game. By default these attributes are only present on the player, but attributes with the <strong>Applicable Entity</strong> type <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">LivingEntity</code> can be attached to any living entity with datapacks - see <a href="dataattributes-1.18.2_datapacks">Data Attributes</a>.</p>

